79223,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"唔係唔認輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係明顯有舞弊<br />\n如果搞清楚冇舞弊都賴死先話人唔認輸啦"},{"pid":"0faae348e865044bc8a63b888c2de4a92fd408de","tid":2279223,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"阿扁出左嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為佢仲喺土城入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dc2d57d9c5fd56f660c6289b93c98f87518a5b","tid":2279223,"uid":280329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你條廢老幾時服輸返入去坐呀"},{"pid":"e7baa80957fae16d082f2e062ac98dae542307eb","tid":2279223,"uid":268537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"因為弱國無外交，台灣人冇揀錯嘅機會<br />\n要形容就好似hocc支持民主黨，黎智英支持共和黨咁<br />\n拜登贏咗就黎智英食死貓，同美國佬講立場係香港主流<br />\n侵赢咗就係hocc做醜人，蘋果日報先係代表香港民意<br />\n咁無論邊邊赢，我哋都以最少代價跟啱大隊"},{"pid":"3838497a767ee2afc8a140b1a56fa25790d702f8","tid":2279223,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"你嗰粒神秘子彈都未解釋到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2286328391c2758c410351474c8be066699022c","tid":2279223,"uid":262095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"衝出黎....."},{"pid":"ba8a7eab757f4e1ee62fae145c8e591f7f3ad61d","tid":2279223,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"佢識唔識咩叫公平選擧"},{"pid":"b6acc4fa24e9865686900d5f60d74f4e5cd5c309","tid":2279223,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"同民主黨一樣作弊貪腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffaffe